<list id="fs-id1164567113313" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha"><item><emphasis effect="italics">r</emphasis> = 0.567 and the sample size, <emphasis effect="italics">n</emphasis>, is 19.<newline count="2"/>
To solve this problem, first find the degrees of freedom. <emphasis effect="italics">df</emphasis> = <emphasis effect="italics">n</emphasis> - 2 = 17.<newline/>
